}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== WET610N v1.0 serial numbers appear to start with '''PUA0'''.
"WST-703S Rev UC" is silkscreened on the board. This follows U-MEDIA convention and this is presumed to be a U-MEDIA device.
By default, the device requests for an IP via DHCP. 169.254.1.250 is the default IP if DHCP requests fail.
The hardware is the same as the [[Linksys WAP610N]].
GPL code is mirrored [http://download.modem-help.co.uk/mfcs-L/LinkSys/WET610N/GPL/ here] at Modem-Help. The files do not appear to be available from Cisco/Linksys' [http://homesupport.cisco.com/en-us/gplcodecenter GPL code center].
